<paragraph id="55DCB9CB9B59D1EF9B3EEF7F71B8417A" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">
Mexico, Nuevo 
<normalizedToken id="EA10D5B20A18CBC70BEB50A1DF250BF6" originalValue="León">Leon</normalizedToken>
, Municipio de Galeana, collected in pine woods on the Peak of Cerro 
<normalizedToken id="1E184E0D1D87EFAA4AF16919C7D3F869" originalValue="Potosí">Potosi</normalizedToken>
, 21 Jul 1935, 
<emphasis id="26036472A9F7F3C7F4CCBCCE28BBCC83" italics="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">C.H. Meuller 2251</emphasis>
(holotype: US-1645320!; isotypes: GH!, US-1646008!).
</paragraph>
